<h1><a href="/glossary.php">Glossary</a> - Bibliography</h1>
<p>an essay bibliography serves to provide a short and specific overview of the research used to write on a topic. As such, the annotated bibliography summarizes all research sources and accesses their value or validity in terms of the written task.</p>
<p>Each of the sources listed comes accompanied with a citation and is extended by a paragraph. How you write the citations, format the bibliography, or organize the research will depend on the style required in the task instructions. Based on the requirements of the lecturers or the academic institution, the bibliography will follow the pre-set standards to present all citations and sources.</p>
<p>Whatever the requested style or formal is, the student must follow the specific requirements and general rules, as well as create a very formal, mistake-free piece of academic writing.</p>
